## Remarks  
 You can set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> in order to specify alternate credentials with which to access the information in Active Directory Domain Services. Any other <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> objects retrieved from this instance (for example, through <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>) are automatically created with the same alternate credentials.  



